scoring the film a GREAT.

00:02:51.450 --> 00:02:54.590
Despite some story flaws, I too loved the
characters in this picture, and laugh every

00:02:54.590 --> 00:02:55.680
time I watch.

00:02:55.680 --> 00:02:56.440
It's a GREAT movie.

